projectGridLines.title: ONNX Runtime
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Offload the unsupported ops to the host using ONNX Runtime

Skill sets: C/C++, Design Patterns, Pytorch, Sound knowledge on Algorithms & Data

Structures, ONNX Runtime.

Expected learning: Familiarity with ML frameworks & HW Architecture

Specific courses required for project execution: Compilers, Operating Systems are good

to have, but not a must
